---
/** Static "About" content with three parts:
 *  - Our Mission -> MAIN QUEST
 *  - How It Works -> GUILD STRUCTURE
 *  - Join Us -> JOIN THE PARTY
 */
---

<section class="container-page my-10 md:my-14">
  <div class="relative">
    <!-- Background Decor -->
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-20 -left-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[var(--brand)]/10 blur-[100px]">
    </div>
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]/10 blur-[100px]"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- MAIN QUEST (Mission) -->
    <div class="relative mb-24 text-center">
      <div
        class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-[var(--brand)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-4 py-1.5 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_var(--brand)]"
      >
        <span class="font-pixel text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-[var(--brand)] uppercase">
          Current Objective
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-pixel text-4xl tracking-tight text-[var(--text)] md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">UBC GAME DEV</h1>
      <p class="font-pixel mt-4 text-xl tracking-widest text-[var(--brand)] uppercase">The Main Quest</p>

      <div
        class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-4xl rounded-2xl border-2 border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface-2)]/50 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm md:p-12"
      >
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)] md:text-2xl">
          "To equip every student with the tools, knowledge, and party members needed to craft their own legendary video
          games."
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-2">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--text-muted)]/20"></div>
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--text-muted)]/20"></div>
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--text-muted)]/20"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- GUILD STRUCTURE (How It Works) -->
    <div class="relative mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-pixel mb-12 text-center text-3xl text-[var(--text)] md:text-4xl">Guild Structure</h2>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Class: Project Teams -->
        <div
          class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-2 border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface-2)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[var(--brand)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(168,85,247,0.15)]"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-20">
            <svg
              class="h-32 w-32"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zm0 9l2.5-1.25L12 8.5l-2.5 1.25L12 11zm0 2.5l-5-2.5-5 2.5L12 22l10-8.5-5-2.5-5 2.5z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8">
            <div
              class="font-pixel mb-4 inline-block rounded bg-[var(--brand)]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-[var(--brand)]"
            >
              Class: Vanguard
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-pixel mb-4 text-2xl text-[var(--text)]">Project Teams</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]">
              Elite squads led by veteran developers. These parties are balanced with diverse skill sets—programmers,
              artists, and designers—working together to ship original titles.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="rounded border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase"
              >
                High EXP
              </span>
              <span
                class="rounded border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase"
              >
                Teamwork
              </span>
              <span
                class="rounded border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase"
              >
                Shipped Games
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Class: Learning Community -->
        <div
          class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-2 border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface-2)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(232,121,249,0.15)]"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-20">
            <svg
              class="h-32 w-32"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"></path><path
                d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"
              >
              </path><path
                d="M12 14l-5-2.778v5.556l5 2.778 5-2.778v-5.556L12 14z"
                opacity=".5"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8">
            <div
              class="font-pixel mb-4 inline-block rounded bg-[var(--accent)]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-[var(--accent)]"
            >
              Class: Recruit
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-pixel mb-4 text-2xl text-[var(--text)]">Learning Community</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]">
              The training grounds for aspiring devs. A safe zone to grind skills, experiment with mechanics, and find
              future party members. No prior level requirement.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="rounded border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase"
              >
                Workshops
              </span>
              <span
                class="rounded border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase"
              >
                Socials
              </span>
              <span
                class="rounded border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase"
              >
                Networking
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- JOIN THE PARTY -->
    <div
      class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface-2)]/30 p-12 text-center"
    >
      <h2 class="font-pixel mb-6 text-3xl text-[var(--text)]">Ready to Join the Party?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-[var(--text-muted)]">
        Whether you're a LVL 1 Beginner or a LVL 99 Expert, there's a spot for you in our guild. Equip your creativity
        and start your adventure today.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-[var(--brand)] px-8 py-4 font-bold text-white shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgb(147,51,234)] transition-all hover:translate-y-1 hover:shadow-none"
      >
        <span class="font-pixel relative z-10 tracking-wider">PRESS START</span>
        <svg
          class="relative z-10 h-5 w-5"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"
          >
          </path><path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
          >
          </path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
